headline: Lockheed's Unit Secures Contract to Aid US Navy and Australia
summary: LMT's unit, Rotary and Mission Systems, secures a contract to support AEGIS modernization, DDG-51 new construction and the allied navy's new production requirements.

headline: Leidos Reveals Its Latest Sea Dart Unmanned Undersea Vessel
summary: LDOS presents Sea Dart, an uncrewed underwater vessel that will help the U.S. Navy and commercial clients in a range of operations.
